short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: COVID-19 (CoronaVirus) broadcast in real time on an interactive dashboard with data available for download

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: In this extension you can track in real time the situation in the world with Coronavirus. COVID-19 statistics will be displayed in your new tab. On the map you can find your country and find out the number of infected dead and cured people from Corona Virus ( COVID 19). Quick access coronavirus information
